te latency (72.6s) and a 5.3x increase from normal.\n\n2. **Cart Service and Redis are severely impacted**: \n   - CartService operations show extreme latency increases (27.4x and 21.9x)\n   - Redis HMSET operations show 43.4x latency increase, indicating database-level issues\n\n3. **Cascading effects**: The high latency in downstream services (PaymentService, CartService/Redis) is causing upstream services like CheckoutService to experience significant delays.\n\n4. **Root cause pattern**: The evidence suggests the issue originates from the payment processing system, which then cascades to affect cart operations and email confirmations.\n\nThe most likely root cause is a **Payment Service degradation** that caused a domino effect throughout the checkout flow, with Redis database operations being particularly severely impacted.\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet\n\n--- Metric Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nDISAGREED\n================================\n请基于上述全量信息以及你的 Trace 数据，对当前故障进行分析。\n重点：请在返回 JSON 的 'stance' 字段中明确标记 'SUPPORT', 'OPPOSE' 或 'NEUTRAL'。", "raw_trace_result": {"status": "success", "message": "成功加载trace数据。UUID: 535dd1bd-273，共 19 个异常组合，0 个状态组合", "filtered_traces": "node_name,service_name,parent_pod,child_pod,operation_name,normal_avg_duration,anomaly_avg_duration,anomaly_count\naiops-k8s-04,checkoutservice,checkoutservice-0,checkoutservice-0,hipstershop.PaymentService/Charge,13679.169223201487,72622.0,出现次数:2\naiops-k8s-03,cartservice,checkoutservice-0,cartservice-0,POST /hipstershop.CartService/EmptyCart,2569.200339366516,70485.0,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-03,redis,cartservice-0,cartservice-0,HMSET,1573.061323856106,69510.0,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-05,cartservice,checkoutservice-0,cartservice-1,POST /hipstershop.CartService/GetCart,2556.877784026997,56978.0,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-08,cartservice,checkoutservice-0,cartservice-2,P